49.0
====

GNOME Tweaks 49.0 comes with no changes since 49.rc.

49.rc
=====

GNOME Tweaks 49.rc comes with the following improvements:

* Contributions:
  - widgets: Fix gsettings which are loaded from non-system directories (Evan Welsh)
  - appearance: Display Shell-related errors as a subtitle (Evan Welsh)
  - Ensure GSettingsTweakFontRow saves the updated preference (Evan Welsh)
  - Update links in app metadata (Vaishnavi Nawghare)
  - Add CI (Maximiliano Sandoval)
  - Add metainfo, desktop and gschema tests (Maximiliano Sandoval)
  - Add D-Bus service file (Ball√≥ Gy√∂rgy)
  - flatpak: Allow dconf to work inside sandbox (Maximiliano Sandoval)
  - data: Change component type to "desktop-application" (AsciiWolf)

* Bugs fixed:
  - #223 Ctrl Q does not close the Tweaks application (Danial Behzadi)
  - #481 After update to 46, themes no longer show up despite that the user
    themes extension is enabled (Evan Welsh)
  - #482 Gnome Tweaks 46.beta not saving new font selection (Evan Welsh)

